{"tid":272250,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[開箱］Microsoft Universal Foldable Keyboard","createTime":"2017-06-05T16:31:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-05T16:31:51.000Z","uid":26922,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1101ce2e27a16f4a56c125aaf2a964ad2cfdd532","tid":272250,"uid":26922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T16:31:51.000Z","msg":"最近買左部ipad pro9.7，想睇下係咪真係可以取代電腦，用落覺得如果本身無咩要求，只係每日睇下片咁，其實幾好用，但發覺每次打字都會無左半個mon <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ...  如果要覆message,打email真係... 幾辛苦，因為你會miss左好多野...<br />\n<br />\n如是者一直搵緊個可以帶得出街又唔會咁重既keyboard, 市面上有好幾款標示自己係portable keyboard，用個陣係舒服因爲個size係full keyboard lay out但唔用個陣就會發覺帶住個keyboard係身同帶住部手提電腦無分別，太厚..<br />\n<br />\n最後決定左買呢款<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/05/235225_79451b911d5be1438eb7179f95673b06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F05%2F235225_79451b911d5be1438eb7179f95673b06.jpg&h=fbc0a3f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n規格如下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （取自官網）<br />\n1<br />\n專為您的平板電腦和智能手機而設。<br />\n將鍵盤與任何兩個兼容裝置配對，輕輕一點即可在兩個裝置之間切換。<br />\n<br />\n2<br />\n兼容多種裝置<br />\nUniversal Foldable Keyboard《萬用折疊式鍵盤》專為配合 iPad、iPhone、Android、Windows 平板電腦及 Windows Phone 裝置使用而設計。<br />\n<br />\n3<br />\n防潑水設計<br />\n防水按鍵組及布料可於意外發生時提供保護作用。<br />\n<br />\n4<br />\n輕巧、摺疊式設計<br />\n創新、折疊式設計讓您可輕易地將鍵盤放入手提包、背包或口袋中。<br />\n<br />\n5<br />\n超薄輕巧<br />\n厚度僅 5 毫米，創新的折疊式設計可讓設備輕易地放入手提包、背包或口袋中。<br />\n<br />\n6<br />\n全尺寸按鍵組<br />\n全尺寸按鍵組給您迅速、舒適的打字體驗。<br />\n<br />\n*一般使用下，電池壽命長達 3 個月<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n開箱圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/05/235443_ec6d430f07bdc5240b9350c856d1b648.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F05%2F235443_ec6d430f07bdc5240b9350c856d1b648.jpg&h=441acbd6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/05/235453_6be3634274fd13c6355d0d1324706e34.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F05%2F235453_6be3634274fd13c6355d0d1324706e34.jpg&h=754dd50c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/05/235458_7f5c9d0ab088ffb37f98a2dae3e57181.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F05%2F235458_7f5c9d0ab088ffb37f98a2dae3e57181.jpg&h=56319ba7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n3年保養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁有信心？！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/05/235709_d7144d67582a577e0c28b47605c3e185.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F05%2F235709_d7144d67582a577e0c28b47605c3e185.jpg&h=55ca17e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n磁力開合<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/06/000009_1309277978dc3f09cf48ae13669facd7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F06%2F000009_1309277978dc3f09cf48ae13669facd7.jpg&h=3bfbbd67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唯一既配對說明書...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/06/001136_d7f97fa5cea087b9e1a5c8a98db15b81.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F06%2F001136_d7f97fa5cea087b9e1a5c8a98db15b81.jpg&h=700f5705&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/06/001139_876a0dffafde628d0ddd1f71afe8fdfc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F06%2F001139_876a0dffafde628d0ddd1f71afe8fdfc.jpg&h=cd2e88bd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/06/001141_051c0390dd9a3b986412541976ed8fd7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F06%2F001141_051c0390dd9a3b986412541976ed8fd7.jpg&h=813df561&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/06/001143_75e5eefd67d260dfe5bd0da12026a370.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F06%2F001143_75e5eefd67d260dfe5bd0da12026a370.jpg&h=84c9e45e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/06/001145_6d3c5ed85dac254e0e95169e2f584b40.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F06%2F001145_6d3c5ed85dac254e0e95169e2f584b40.jpg&h=eb999427&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/06/001218_df36e9b365cf0f154861b409f27f17fb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F06%2F001218_df36e9b365cf0f154861b409f27f17fb.jpg&h=c0ed35dd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/06/001221_71af816d071afd4dba9f7845a45a1b95.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F06%2F001221_71af816d071afd4dba9f7845a45a1b95.jpg&h=793157c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n總結：<br />\n打字慣左鍵盤有闊間距，今日岩岩開，用左一陣唔係幾慣，有時打得太快會打錯字，而且某幾個字既大細會唔一樣，鍵身打落去有回彈感，上網睇有人話似surface keyboard,本身無用因爲太貴所以唔知似唔似，相信本身個keyboard 可以摺埋同埋唔重應該係最大既賣點<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">買左460</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}